<L>__{9: exterior hillside. springfield street. eureka. day.}
<A>__{a chevrolet zig zags up a shabby canyon. it's the road to the city dump. its final bend reveals a line of bellowing garbage trucks. everything is backed up. nothing moves except the car. the cause of the hold up is explained at the top. a sheriff's car blocks the road. a uniform moves to wave the chevrolet in.}
